"'''A Buyer's Guide to Alternative Starships'''" is a roleplaying game source article from [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 5]], written from the point of view of an unnamed [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] who needed a ship and was talking to a [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] known as [[C-D20]] and his [[Counterpart/Legends|counterpart]], [[R2-RD]]. The story introduced several models of starships. It also included brief sidebars involving the [[Z-10 Seeker-class scout ship|Z-10]] and [[Helix-class light interceptor|Helix]], and a fake ad for the [[ZH-25 Questor-class light freighter|ZH-25]].

